3601.43 and 3538.00 reflecting erratic behavior of the shares in a
low volume on the BSE market following alternative bouts of buying
and selling.
</P>
<P>
Operators had turned cautious due to the United Front's demand
for dissolution of the Lok Sabha (Lower House of Parliament)
immediately to end the political impasse in the country.
</P>
<P>
The rupee's continued fall was the main cause of concern for
foreign funds, who were not willing to enter the market in the
prevailing political instability and approaching year end.
</P>
