Brazil's Cruzeiro 2-0 to win the third straight title of the
Intercontinental Championship for Europe here on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
The underdogs Cruzeiro settled in quickly and staged a series
of attacks begging a goal in the opening ten minutes, only seeing
their attemps blocked by Dortmund goalie Stefan Klos with majestic
diving saves.
</P>
<P>
