each year to review and discuss economic and trade issues between
the two places. Co-chairmen of the ongoing 20th joint Plenary
Session are Raymond Chien, chairman of the Hong Kong-Japan
committee, and Tomiichi Akiyama, chairman of the Japan-Hong Kong
committee.  
