<TEXT>
<P>
HEFEI, December 2 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese University of Science
and Technology in Hefei, capital of east China's Anhui Province,
recently opened a Cerebral Science Research Center.
</P>
<P>
Tang Xiaowei, a noted expert on cerebral science and
academician with the Chinese Academy of Sciences, serves as the
director of the center.
</P>
<P>
