China's longest river. The province's abundant hydropower
resources, estimated at 150 million kilowatts, account for close
to 25 percent of the national total.
</P>
<P>
ABB has cooperated with Sichuan in construction of key state
projects, including the Panzhihua Iron and Steel Co. and the Ertan
Power Station.  
