<HEADLINE> Beijing Newspapers Highlights </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 2 (Xinhua) -- Highlights of today's major
Beijing-based newspapers:
</P>
<P>
 "People's Daily"
</P>
