<HEADLINE> Groupings for 1st World Squash Doubles Championships </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, December 2 (Xinhua) -- Following are the groupings
for the preliminary rounds of the men's and women's doubles
events at the 400,000 HK dollar (51,200 US dollars) first World
