Men's Doubles:
</P>
<P>
Group A: Australia, Pakistan, Hong Kong, Canada, United States
and the Netherlands.
</P>
<P>
Group B: Britain, New Zealand, Malaysia, Singapore, South
Africa and Scotland.
</P>
<P>
Women's doubles:
</P>
<P>
Group A: Australia, South Africa, Canada, Malaysia, United
States and the Philippines;
</P>
<P>
Group B: Britain, New Zealand, Scotland, Japan, Hong Kong and
Singapore.
</P>
<P>
(Top two teams of each group enter semi-finals.)  
</P>
